FuncDef: This command specifies the number of WLAN-GW IOMs used as active IOMs from the total number of configured WLAN-GW IOMs. If there are more configured IOM than active-iom-limit, then the remaining number of IOMs is designated as backup(s).

ParaDef.Info: Specifies the number of IOMs in this WLAN Gateway ISA group that are intended for active use. Values-1 to 3.
